#: ../../docs/classes/class_environment.rst:213
msgid "enum **BGMode**:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/classes/class_environment.rst:215
msgid ""
"**BG_CLEAR_COLOR** = **0** --- Clears the background using the clear "
"color defined in "
":ref:`ProjectSettings.rendering/environment/default_clear_color "
"<class_ProjectSettings_property_rendering/environment/default_clear_color>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/classes/class_environment.rst:217
msgid "**BG_COLOR** = **1** --- Clears the background using a custom clear color."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/classes/class_environment.rst:219
msgid "**BG_SKY** = **2** --- Displays a user-defined sky in the background."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/classes/class_environment.rst:221
msgid ""
"**BG_CANVAS** = **3** --- Displays a :ref:`CanvasLayer "
"<class_CanvasLayer>` in the background."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/classes/class_environment.rst:223
msgid ""
"**BG_KEEP** = **4** --- Keeps on screen every pixel drawn in the "
"background. This is the fastest background mode, but it can only be "
"safely used in fully-interior scenes (no visible sky or sky reflections)."
" If enabled in a scene where the background is visible, \"ghost trail\" "
"artifacts will be visible when moving the camera."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/classes/class_environment.rst:225
msgid "**BG_CAMERA_FEED** = **5** --- Displays a camera feed in the background."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/classes/class_environment.rst:227
msgid ""
"**BG_MAX** = **6** --- Represents the size of the :ref:`BGMode "
"<enum_Environment_BGMode>` enum."
msgstr ""

